类 DoubleRouteNet

  • java.lang.Object
    • zhao.algorithmMagic.operands.coordinateNet.DoubleRouteNet
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable, Cloneable, RouteNet<DoubleCoordinateMany,DoubleConsanguinityRoute>, Operands<RouteNet<DoubleCoordinateMany,DoubleConsanguinityRoute>>

    public class DoubleRouteNet
extends Object
implements RouteNet<DoubleCoordinateMany,DoubleConsanguinityRoute>
    Java类于 2022/10/19 17:07:38 创建

    Double类型的多维线路网，存储的都是Double类型的多维线路对象，其中的每一个坐标维度可以是任意的，但是需要每一个坐标的维度数量保持一致！

    The Double-type multidimensional line network stores all Double-type multidimensional line objects. Each coordinate dimension can be arbitrary, but the number of dimensions of each coordinate needs to be consistent!

    作者:
    zhao
